<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document Verification Failed</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background:#f4f7fa; color:#444;">

    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600"
        style="margin:30px auto; border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); background:#fff;">
        <tbody>

            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
                <td align="center" bgcolor="#d9534f"
                    style="padding:20px; color:#fff; font-size:22px; font-weight:bold;">
                    iDispatch - Document Verification Failed
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Body -->
            <tr>
                <td style="padding:30px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#444;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 15px;">Hello <strong>
                            <%= userName %>
                        </strong>,</p>

                    <p style="margin:0 0 15px;">
                        We regret to inform you that the documents you provided for your driver profile verification
                        did not meet our requirements. As a result, your verification could not be completed.
                    </p>

                    <p style="margin:0 0 15px;">
                        To proceed, please log in to your account and upload the correct and valid documents. Ensure
                        that
                        the files are clear, up-to-date, and match the required criteria.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Call to Action Button -->
                    <p style="text-align:center; margin:25px 0;">
                        <a href="<%= baseUrl %>login"
                            style="background:#d9534f; color:#fff; padding:12px 25px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-weight:bold; display:inline-block;">
                            Resubmit Documents
                        </a>
                    </p>

                    <p style="margin:0 0 15px;">
                        If you believe this was a mistake or need further guidance, please contact our support team for
                        assistance.
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
                <td align="center" bgcolor="#f1f1f1" style="padding:15px; font-size:12px; color:#888;">
                    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> iDispatch Mobility. All rights reserved.
                        <br />
                        Need help? Contact us at
                        <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color:#d9534f; text-decoration:none;">
                            <%= supportEmail %>
                        </a>.
                </td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>

</html>